data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $5000 IN CLOSING ASSISTANCE WITH REASONABLE OFFER!! This Charming home is situated on 2.09 acres in Tall Timbers addition just outside of the city limits featuring 5 Bedrooms and 3 baths. Great kitchen with island and unique brick design. Spacious living area with woodburning fireplace. Large master including master bath with double closets. Den/Sunroom features lots of extra space with natural lighting that leads out to fenced in back yard with inground saltwater pool and patio area! Property also includes 1500 Sq ft metal shop and detached carport (2 car).
